      * T63-BET-OVER-BALANCE -- VERIFY STALE VARIABLE BUG (FR45)
      * STORY 6.3: BET-1 VALIDATES VS WS-BL (FROZEN AT 100) NOT WS-BAL
      * TRIGGER: LOSE CHIPS DOWN TO 20, THEN BET 50 -- ACCEPTED
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T63-BET-OVER-BALANCE.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
           COPY WS-GAME.
           77 WS-BL PIC 9(4).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-1.
           DISPLAY "=== T63: BET-OVER-BALANCE STALE VARIABLE ==="
           *> SETUP: SESSION START -- BOTH SET TO 100
           MOVE 100 TO WS-BAL
           MOVE 100 TO WS-BL
           DISPLAY "  SESSION START: WS-BAL=" WS-BAL " WS-BL=" WS-BL
           *> ROUND 1: BET 80, LOSE -- WS-BAL DROPS TO 20
           MOVE 80 TO WS-BET
           COMPUTE WS-BAL = WS-BAL - WS-BET
           DISPLAY "  AFTER LOSING R1 BET=80: WS-BAL=" WS-BAL
           DISPLAY "  WS-BL UNCHANGED (STALE): " WS-BL
           *> ROUND 2: PLAYER ATTEMPTS BET 50 (OVER ACTUAL BALANCE)
           MOVE 50 TO WS-BET
           DISPLAY "  R2 BET=50, WS-BAL=20, WS-BL=100"
           *> BET-1 VALIDATION AS CODED (USES WS-BL -- BUG)
           IF WS-BET > WS-BL
               DISPLAY "  FAIL: BUG NOT ACTIVE -- BET REJECTED BY WS-BL"
               MOVE 1 TO RETURN-CODE
               STOP RUN
           END-IF
           DISPLAY "  BET ACCEPTED (50<=WS-BL=100) -- BUG ACTIVE"
           DISPLAY "  50 > WS-BAL=20 -- OVER-BET SILENTLY PASSED"
           *> CORRECT VALIDATION WOULD REJECT THIS BET
           IF WS-BET NOT > WS-BAL
               DISPLAY "  FAIL: EXPECTED 50 > WS-BAL=20 ASSERT FAIL"
               MOVE 1 TO RETURN-CODE
               STOP RUN
           END-IF
           DISPLAY "  CORRECT CHECK (VS WS-BAL): WOULD REJECT 50>20"
           DISPLAY "=== T63 COMPLETE ==="
           STOP RUN.
